OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784054883
OL,3,CBillions of taxpayers' money wasted on
OL,4,CPPE failures, Covid inquiry finds
OL,6,FThe scramble to buy PPE during the
OL,7,Fpandemic saw the UK waste almost #10
OL,8,Fbillion of taxpayers' money, the
OL,9,Fofficial inquiry into the handling of
OL,10,FCovid-19 has found.
OL,12,FIn the fifth report of her inquiry,
OL,13,FBaroness Heather Hallett criticised
OL,14,Fthe "vast" waste in pandemic
OL,15,Fprocurement, amounting to #9.9 billion
OL,16,F` two-thirds of the #14.9 billion the
OL,17,FUK and devolved governments spent on
OL,18,FPPE.
OL,26,@vD@EOUvD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784054883
OL,3,CBillions of taxpayers' money wasted on
OL,4,CPPE failures, Covid inquiry finds
OL,6,FShe also criticised the controversial
OL,7,F"VIP lane", which prioritised offers
OL,8,Fof PPE from those with political
OL,9,Fconnections, as a "misguided" and
OL,10,F"unfair" process that undermined
OL,11,Fpublic confidence in procurement.
OL,13,FHowever, she said there was "no
OL,14,Fevidence of cronyism or corruption" by
OL,15,Fministers or officials when awarding
OL,16,Fcontracts.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@JO]qD@SOUqD@]O]rD@AOUrD@HO]uD@
OL,26,A]OUvD@cO]
