OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784054883
OL,3,CBillions of taxpayers' money wasted on
OL,4,CPPE failures, Covid inquiry finds
OL,6,FHallett said: "The waste of taxpayers'
OL,7,Fmoney was vast. The public must be
OL,8,Fable to trust that their money is
OL,9,Fbeing spent with propriety, fairness
OL,10,Fand transparency.
OL,12,F"Public confidence ` so important in
OL,13,Fan emergency ` was undermined by
OL,14,Ffailures in procurement."
OL,16,FIn her report, Hallett found the UK
OL,17,Fwas underprepared for the pandemic,
OL,18,Fwith existing stockpiles of PPE "in a
OL,19,Fperilous state", with large quantities
OL,20,Fof expired equipment.
OL,26,@nD@OOUtD@AOUvD@YO]zD@aOU{D@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784054883
OL,3,CBillions of taxpayers' money wasted on
OL,4,CPPE failures, Covid inquiry finds
OL,6,FShe found only a third of the masks in
OL,7,FEngland's pre-pandemic stockpile were
OL,8,Fusable, while Scotland had no supplies
OL,9,Fof the top-level FFP3 masks needed by
OL,10,Fhealthcare professionals.
OL,12,FThe report describes a procurement
OL,13,Fsystem working under "immense
OL,14,Fpressure", with no effective system
OL,15,Ffor triaging offers of PPE.
OL,17,FThat system was "deluged" with offers
OL,18,Fafter Boris Johnson and then-health
OL,19,Fsecretary Matt Hancock issued a "call
OL,20,Fto arms" for PPE in April 2020.
OL,26,@uD@VOUvD@IO]yD@QOUyD@YO]{D@aOU|D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784054883
OL,3,CBillions of taxpayers' money wasted on
OL,4,CPPE failures, Covid inquiry finds
OL,6,FOfficials told the inquiry the call to
OL,7,Farms had "made matters worse", with
OL,8,Fthe procurement system receiving
OL,9,F25,000 offers over 15 weeks, including
OL,10,F300 offers a day at some points.
OL,12,FAgainst that background, officials
OL,13,Festablished a "high priority" or "VIP"
OL,14,Flane that prioritised offers that had
OL,15,Fbeen referred by politicians,
OL,16,Fhealthcare leaders and others.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
