OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784054883
OL,3,CBillions of taxpayers' money wasted on
OL,4,CPPE failures, Covid inquiry finds
OL,6,FHallett described the VIP lane as "a
OL,7,Fmisguided attempt at prioritisation
OL,8,Fthat embedded unfairness in emergency
OL,9,Fprocurement" that saw offers from
OL,10,Fpolitically-connected individuals more
OL,11,Flikely to receive a contract than
OL,12,Fothers.
OL,14,FShe said contracts awarded through the
OL,15,FVIP lane were "more expensive" and had
OL,16,Fmore "contract performance issues"
OL,17,Fthan those awarded through the normal
OL,18,Froute.
OL,26,@nD@cOUqD@LO]wD@OOUwD@^O]xD@FOUxD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784054883
OL,3,CBillions of taxpayers' money wasted on
OL,4,CPPE failures, Covid inquiry finds
OL,6,FThe report found that, of the 32
OL,7,Fpeople who referred successful offers
OL,8,Fto the VIP lane, 15 had a connection
OL,9,Fwith the Conservative Party and none
OL,10,Fcame from any other party, although
OL,11,Fpoliticians from other parties were
OL,12,Freferred to it.
OL,14,FHallett said her inquiry had found "no
OL,15,Fevidence of cronyism or corruption on
OL,16,Fthe part of ministers or officials in
OL,17,Fthe final decision of whether to award
OL,18,For reject a contract", but noted the
OL,19,Fsystem was "inherently biased towards
OL,20,Fthose with connections to the UK
OL,21,Fgovernment".
OL,26,@vD@dOUzD@UO]{D@LOU}D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
