CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784054883
OL,3,CBillions of taxpayers' money wasted on
OL,4,CPPE failures, Covid inquiry finds
OL,6,FShe said: "This heightened the risk of
OL,7,Fabuse. It damaged the reputation of
OL,8,Fthose involved in procurement during
OL,9,Fthe pandemic and undermined public
OL,10,Ftrust in the UK government's emergency
OL,11,Fprocurement system, in the UK
OL,12,Fgovernment itself and in its response
OL,13,Fto the pandemic.
OL,15,F"The High Priority Lane should not be
OL,16,Frepeated."
OL,26,@nD@KOUwD@AOUxD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
