OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784054883
OL,3,CBillions of taxpayers' money wasted on
OL,4,CPPE failures, Covid inquiry finds
OL,6,FNicola Brook, a solicitor at law firm
OL,7,FBroudie Jackson Canter, which
OL,8,Frepresents the Covid-19 Bereaved
OL,9,FFamilies for Justice UK campaign
OL,10,Fgroup, decribed the findings as
OL,11,F"shocking".
OL,13,F"Today's report reveals the shocking
OL,14,Flevel of corruption and cronyism at
OL,15,Fthe heart of government, resulting in
OL,16,Fbillions of pounds lost as companies
OL,17,Fsought to profit while thousands
OL,18,Fdied," she said.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784054883
OL,3,CBillions of taxpayers' money wasted on
OL,4,CPPE failures, Covid inquiry finds
OL,6,F"What is equally shocking is the
OL,7,Fchair's failure to call this
OL,8,Fcorruption out after she inexplicably
OL,9,Ffailed to call crucial witnesses
OL,10,Finvolved in some of the most
OL,11,Fscandalous contracts."
OL,13,FDuring the inquiry's investigation
OL,14,Finto procurement, Hallett also heard
OL,15,Fevidence on PPE Medpro, which was
OL,16,Fordered to repay #148 million to the
OL,17,FGovernment last year after the High
OL,18,FCourt found it had breached a contract
OL,19,Fto supply millions of surgical gowns.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784054883
OL,3,CBillions of taxpayers' money wasted on
OL,4,CPPE failures, Covid inquiry finds
OL,6,FBut Tuesday's report did not include
OL,7,Fher findings on Medpro due to an
OL,8,Fongoing National Crime Agency (NCA)
OL,9,Finvestigation into the firm, which is
OL,10,Flinked to Conservative peer Baroness
OL,11,FMichelle Mone via her husband Doug
OL,12,FBarrowman.
OL,14,FBoth Lady Mone, 54, and Mr Barrowman,
OL,15,F61, deny wrongdoing.JA Downing Street
OL,16,Fspokeswoman said the report made for
OL,17,F"difficult reading".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
