OL,3,CBillions of taxpayers' money wasted on
OL,4,CPPE failures, Covid inquiry finds
OL,6,F"We will, of course, carefully
OL,7,Fconsider the inquiry's recommendations
OL,8,Fin detail, and we will respond in due
OL,9,Fcourse," she said.
